data.description: Welcome to this impressive former builder model home with upgrades that will leave you in awe. Situated in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this 4-bedroom, 2 and a half bath house offers the perfect blend of luxury and functionality.     Step into the heart of the home, where the kitchen boasts a commercial-grade 42-inch 6-burner stove, griddle, and vent hood. You'll also find a KitchenAid Superba dual oven, built-in microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator. The brick backsplash, granite counters, and solid cherry and glass cabinets create a stunning culinary space.     Entertain guests in the large formal dining room or gather around the fireplace with gas logs in living room. The downstairs bonus room, adorned with beautiful French doors, can be transformed into a home office.     As you make your way to the upstairs, you'll discover an additional family room or game room, perfect for creating lasting memories.     The luxurious primary suite features a sitting area with a wine bar and entertainment center, complete with granite counters and cherry wood cabinets. The primary bath boasts a walk-in shower, oversized tub, cherry wood pedestal vanity, and a spacious walk-in closet.     Crown molding and 9-foot ceilings in every room add an elegant touch.     Music enthusiasts will appreciate the whole house audio system, complete with in-ceiling speakers and a 5-source audio controller. The upstairs game room features a 6-speaker surround sound system, perfect for immersing yourself in your favorite movies or games.     Rest easy knowing your home is protected with a hardwired security system, including sensors on every door and window, ready for monitoring. Additionally, a 16-channel Lorex security camera system ensures your peace of mind.     Enjoy the outdoors on the covered patio, complete with built-in speakers and ceiling fan.    A new roof was installed in 2016.     The sale includes top of line Whirlpool steam washer and dryer, stainless steel refrigerator and microwave, as well as a 16x8 shed for extra storage.     Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable home your own. The Connelly Ultimate series pool table with 3-inch slate is not included but negotiable for sale, adding even more entertainment options to this already incredible property.
